key "gerryQO"

\end_inset

) to better understand how a quantum beam-splitter works: we need to satisfy
 
\begin_inset Formula $r^{*}t+r^{'}t^{'}=0$
\end_inset

 so if 
\begin_inset Formula $t=t^{'}=e^{i\Delta}/\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

 then 
\begin_inset Formula $r^{'}=-r^{*}$
\end_inset

.
